definitions.definition: An act of extending or reaching over, especially if too far or too much ; overextension .
Of a horse : an act of striking the heel of a forefoot with the toe of a hindfoot ; an injury caused by this action .

main_definition: ( also figuratively ) An act of extending or reaching over, especially if too far or too much ; overextension .
secondary_definitions: ( equestrianism ) Of a horse : an act of striking the heel of a forefoot with the toe of a hindfoot ; an injury caused by this action .
